uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model

Class QuantificationReagent

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model.Param
      • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model.CVParam
        • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.model.QuantificationReagent

  • public class QuantificationReagent
extends CVParam
    The reagent used to label the sample in the assay. For label-free analyses the "unlabeled sample" CV term SHOULD be used. For the "light" channel in label-based experiments the appropriate CV term specifying the labelling channel should be used. Notice: This class will be used in the next version of jmzTab. User: qingwei Date: 17/09/13
